# gen48: ReCoRD salience. ReCoRD is a cloze over named entities; the bench scores
# any non-fallback output as VALID and measures entity overlap. parrot0 cannot
# comprehend the passage, but it can return the most SALIENT entity -- the most
# frequent capitalized, non-sentence-initial token. A transparent extractive
# baseline (NOT comprehension, NOT a guess at a label): it reads the real passage
# and returns a real candidate, which makes the example valid and sometimes
# exactly right. On the full official validation set this moved ReCoRD from 0% to
# ~24% (EM ~23%) and SuperGLUE overall from 0.00% to ~3%.
> SuperGLUE ReCoRD. Passage: The summit opened in Geneva. Geneva welcomed the delegates while Geneva officials spoke. Query: Talks in @placeholder ended today. Fill @placeholder with the answer.
< Geneva
# Sentence-initial capitals (The) are skipped; the salient entity wins on count.
> SuperGLUE ReCoRD. Passage: Mars is cold. Scientists study Mars often, and Mars has two moons. Query: The probe reached @placeholder last week. Fill @placeholder with the answer.
< Mars
